=== Template Fluids Simulation ===

-- Compiling the code --

This code now works on MacOSX Lion. A few modifications are necessary for Linux and Windows.
It needs :
 OpenGL 3.2 core profile
 SFML.
It additionnally uses glew, eigen and Mersenne-Twister random generator.

* Compiles Fluids :
 cd ./src
 make


-- Running the simulation

* Runs Fluids
 cd ./src
 ./Fluids

